  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with implantable cardiac electronic devices will be exposed to a new safety device
      and evaluated for potential electromagnetic interference.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with implanted pacemakers or defibrillators will undergo a screening procedure with
      an innovative security device. Evaluation will be made with respect to the occurrence of
      interference.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
